Package net.explorviz.landscape.model.application

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggregatedClazzCommunication
    Model representing unidirectional communication between classes (from sourceClazz to targetClazz) within a single application.
    Application
    Model representing a single application with a software landscape.
    ApplicationCommunication
    Model representing communication between two Application.
    Clazz
    Model representing a single class (instance during runtime within a single application).
    ClazzCommunication
    Model representing communication between classes (within a single application).
    Component
    Model representing a component (e.g., a package within a java application).
    DatabaseQuery
    Model representing executed database queries.
    Trace
    Model representing a trace containing severals TraceStep between two Clazz.
    TraceStep
    Model representing detailed runtime information for ClazzCommunication between two Clazz in a specific Trace.
